title: 5g not enabled in my country. I am in the Philippines.
content:
Google has disabled 5g in my country.  My sim worked fine on 5g with my non-Pixel phone.  There is an internal list of approved countries.  My carrier supports sub 6.  A warning that it is not supported should be good enough.
I was going to buy a Pixel 6 when available but unless this is fixed I will have to look elsewhere.
